{"tid":2224017,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【專訪】開「Andy is Missing」專頁求救　李宇軒妹妹眼中的兄長，和他未圓的夢","createTime":"2020-09-30T08:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T09:43:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f171e45cf404a921f4d04afce6567f29d02d5574","tid":2224017,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-09_Ujrwk_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-1-09_Ujrwk_1200x0.png&h=eefcd8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>無論與你共度的夏天  將來的夢<br />\n<br />\n還是龐大的希望  我決不忘懷<br />\n<br />\n強忍淚水  笑著說再見<br />\n<br />\n肯定很難受吧</strong><br />\n<br />\n9 月 26 日，李小姐把哥哥李宇軒在日本拍攝的一張照片放上她開設的 &ldquo;Andy is Missing&rdquo; Facebook專頁，又在照片裏附上一段日文歌詞 &mdash; 那是動漫《未聞花名》的片尾曲《secret base ～你給我的東西～》。就像程序員寫的代碼一樣，有一名讀者解讀出來，在底下留言：「加油撐住，不會像歌詞一樣在 10 年後才再見的！」<br />\n<br />\n對外界來講，李宇軒是那個在電視新聞裏被香港警方指涉及勾結外國勢力、被內地公安指懷疑偷渡的香港青年；但對李小姐來說，李宇軒是一個熱愛動漫、成天對著電腦、不愛社交愛安靜的程式員，是一齊成長的哥哥。兩人在兒時感情很好，相比其他同學對家中兄長的抱怨，李小姐發現，自己的哥哥特別懂得照顧自己，願意分享經驗知識，幫妹妹解決各種困難，尤其是電腦方面。長大之後，兄妹比小時候稍微疏遠一點，有各自的生活。長大後的哥哥，在李小姐眼中，仍是喜歡埋頭研究電腦、看漫畫的文靜男生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E9%96%8B-andy-is-missing-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%87%E8%BB%92%E5%A6%B9%E5%A6%B9%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%85%84%E9%95%B7-%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%96%E6%9C%AA%E5%9C%93%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E9%2596%258B-andy-is-missing-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2595%2591-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%2587%25E8%25BB%2592%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E7%259C%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%2584%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259C%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%25A2%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=8363d1e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E9%2596%258B-andy-is-missing-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2595%2591-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%2587%25E8%25BB%2592%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E7%259C%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%2584%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259C%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%25A2%2F&h=136ec534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E9%96%8B-andy-is-missing-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%87%E8%BB%92%E5%A6%B9%E5%A6%B9%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%85%84%E9%95%B7-%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%96%E6%9C%AA%E5%9C%93%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A2/</a>"},{"pid":"c3034ff6ee6cb07ab4056e83c95a1bf9fffd3319","tid":2224017,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1526e8aece658538fd1b0e7bf4eca264946db573","tid":2224017,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30614f3ed3a7b3a72feae701f9042d31c33323c1","tid":2224017,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:33:09.000Z","msg":"對於哥哥的離開，李小姐感慨：「事情發展成這樣，為什麼有一班香港的年輕人會選擇這條路？一個正常的人在什麼情況下，才會覺得 12 個人坐上快艇，衝出大海，是一種合理的選擇？要不他根本不是自願，要不他覺得已經沒有更好的選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n在家屬召開第一次記者會後，李小姐開了「Andy is Missing」這個 Facebook 專頁，她專門用英文寫作，希望引起更多國際關注。她感覺政治人物如黃之鋒、岑敖暉在網絡說一句，作用似乎比自己大很多，但自己也不能什麼都不做，「沒理由每次都要其他人出聲。」"},{"pid":"c011752c49580da5849deadb480156893204c037","tid":2224017,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689359eddb18d56b65e0503cf0b39cc4d1105cc2","tid":2224017,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1526e8aece658538fd1b0e7bf4eca264946db573","tid":2224017,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e002007b6d76dcf2880be9e757619daf7e2145f0","tid":2224017,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d67ae3b5d3654f186e64e1a0b4ccadcd281398d","tid":2224017,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\